data.description: A truly one of a kind !! This property has a great location and is a Must see !! Literally walk to the shopping centers of Florida Ave and Sanderson/Kirby, Hemet Valley Mall. Showing pride of ownership and very well taken care of, many many amenities such a beautiful entrance with stamped concrete, a nice patio and an extra room in the back which is a casita like with a full bed and half a bathroom. A covered barbecue spot for these family gatherings which includes a beautiful outdoor chimney to spend nights in the winter, beautiful landscaped backyard with underground sprinklers system. Great layout with a nice kitchen, quartz countertops. 2 car garage with side access to the back, roof is fairly new, replaced approx. 3 years ago and so much more. All information provided is deemed reliable but is not guaranteed, buyers and buyers agent are encourage to verify any and all information regarding this property, sq ft, permits, etc.
